## Description {#details}

BTF&#95;KIND&#95;FUNC&#95;PROTO are followed by multiple &quot;struct BTFParam&quot;.

The exist number of <a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/btf/btfparam">BTFParam</a> is stored in the vlen (of the info in &quot;struct CommonType&quot;).
